'''Addams''' is a crater  on [[Venus]].<ref name="gpn">{{gpn|50|Addams}}</ref> It was named after [[Jane Addams]].<ref>{{cite book |first=  Norma |last= Olin |title= Index to women of the world from ancient to modern times;: Biographies and portraits (Useful reference series) |date= 1970 |isbn= 978-0873050975 |location= Westwood, Mass |publisher= F. W. Faxon }}</ref>

